---
// Outside of Work section for printable CV
---

<section class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900/60 backdrop-blur-xl border border-gray-900 dark:border-slate-700/50 rounded-3xl transition-all hover:border-indigo-500/30 p-6" aria-labelledby="outside-work-heading">
  <h2 id="outside-work-heading" class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-500 dark:text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm" aria-hidden="true">interests</span>
    Outside of Work
  </h2>

  <div class="space-y-3">
    <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 text-lg mt-0.5" aria-hidden="true">handyman</span>
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-sm mb-1">DIY Woodworking & Carpentry</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
          Building custom furniture and home projects. Combining traditional craftsmanship with modern precision tools.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 text-lg mt-0.5" aria-hidden="true">home_app_logo</span>
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-sm mb-1">Home Automation Systems</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
          Designing and implementing smart home infrastructure. Integrating IoT devices and automation workflows.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400 text-lg mt-0.5" aria-hidden="true">view_in_ar</span>
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-sm mb-1">3D Printing & CAD Modeling</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
          Creating custom CAD models for woodworking jigs and home projects. Rapid prototyping for functional parts.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
